id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fli1665702536446.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fli1665702536446.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fli1665702536446.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fli1665702536446\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Inserts a new occurrence before this occurrence.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"fli1665702536446__topic_d126344e1_d126345e1_d126346e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fli1665702536446__p_d126347e1_d126348e1_d126349e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Return</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Object</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">.<span class=\"keyword apiname\">insertNewBefore()</span>\n</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fli1665702536446__section_w748ab1b5b3_w749ab1b5_w750ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d276448e70\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fli1665702536446__section_w751ab1b5b5_w752ab1b5_w753ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d276448e79\">Return value</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"fli1665702536446__parml_uls_rly_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">Return</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">newly created <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Occurrence</span> object.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fli1665702536446__section_w754ab1b5b7_w755ab1b5_w756ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d276448e100\">Exceptions</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following exceptions may be thrown:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</code> if this occurrence is not valid</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface.OccurrenceCreationException</code> if the entity has non-editable fields </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fli1665702536446__section_w757ab1b5b9_w758ab1b5_w759ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d276448e122\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fli1665702536446__p_d126371e1_d126372e1_d126373e1\">Creates a new occurrence and inserts it right before\n        this one in the list of the Entity's occurrences.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/shk1665703139073.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</a><p>Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wqh1665703141823.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.OccurrenceCreationException</a><p>Exception thrown if the occurrence could not be created.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hfh1665702535808.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Occurrence</a><p>The uniface.Occurrence object provides access to selected properties of the occurrence that it represents. It is returned by the getOccurrence function of the uniface.Entity object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/reb1665702537007.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Entity</a><p>The uniface.Entity object provides access to selected properties of the component entity that it represents. It is returned by the getEntities and getEntity functions of the uniface.Instance and uniface.Occurrence objects.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527565\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527565\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "insertNewBefore() Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 11, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Inserts a new occurrence before this occurrence. Return = Object . insertNewBefore() Arguments None Return value Return newly created uniface.Occurrence object. Exceptions The following exceptions may be thrown: uniface.InvalidDataObjectException if this occurrence is not valid uniface.OccurrenceCreationException if the entity has non-editable fields Description Creates a new occurrence and inserts it right before this one in the list of the Entity's occurrences. Related Links uniface.InvalidDataObjectException Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid. uniface.OccurrenceCreationException Exception thrown if the occurrence could not be created. uniface.Occurrence The uniface.Occurrence object provides access to selected properties of the occurrence that it represents. It is returned by the getOccurrence function of the uniface.Entity object. uniface.Entity The uniface.Entity object provides access to selected properties of the component entity that it represents. It is returned by the getEntities and getEntity functions of the uniface.Instance and uniface.Occurrence objects. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}